# ğŸ§ª Playwright API Automation â€“ CRUD Framework
OVERVIEW
This project demonstrates a **modular API Test Automation Framework** using **Playwright + TypeScript**.  
It performs a full **CRUD flow** (`Create â†’ Read â†’ Update â†’ Delete`) multiple times with **dynamic data** generated using **Faker**.  
The API base URL is configured via `config.properties`.

---

## ğŸš€ Tech Stack

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|----------|
| **Playwright** | API request engine + test runner |
| **TypeScript** | Strong typing & modular architecture |
| **Faker (@faker-js/faker)** | Generate random data for each run |
| **Axios** | HTTP client to send API requests |
| **properties-reader** | To read config from `config.properties` |

