ğŸ” CRUD Flow Summary

Each test iteration performs:

Step	Action	Description
1ï¸âƒ£	POST	
Create a new pet/user with random data

2ï¸âƒ£	GET	
Fetch the created record by ID

3ï¸âƒ£	PUT
Update data dynamically

4ï¸âƒ£	GET	
Validate the updated record

5ï¸âƒ£	DELETE
