âœ… Assertions

Each step validates:
HTTP Status Codes
Response JSON structure
Updated data verification


ğŸ§± Key Concepts

ğŸ”¹Modular Design: Reusable API layers (no hardcoded logic)
ğŸ”¹Faker Integration: Auto-generate new data every execution
ğŸ”¹ Config Driven: Base URL read dynamically from properties file
ğŸ”¹Enum Usage: Clean endpoint management
ğŸ”¹Iterative Flow: Repeats CRUD steps multiple times automatically


